                <li><strong>Enable collective innovation:</strong> Empowering a global community of defenders, researchers, and veterans to continuously enhance the tools protecting our shared infrastructure.</li>
                <li><strong>Ensure auditability and safety:</strong> Allowing operators to inspect every line of code that touches their environment, building confidence that no hidden risks exist.</li>
                <li><strong>Sustain long-term resilience:</strong> Ensuring that open ecosystems endure beyond vendor lifecycles or budget cycles, providing continuity in protection.</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="approach-note">Open source is not a business model — it is a mission principle. It keeps innovation accessible, defenses transparent, and security sustainable, especially for those protecting systems vital to national stability.</p>
            </article>

