              </p>
              <p>We chose Google SecOps because it enables:</p>
              <ul class="approach-bullets">
                <li><strong>Massive Scalability:</strong> Ingests telemetry from hundreds of distributed OT/ICS environments without on-premise overhead.</li>
                <li><strong>AI-Driven Speed:</strong> Integrated Gemini AI accelerates triage, detection, and response, amplifying the impact of small elite teams.</li>
                <li><strong>Unified Data Model (UDM):</strong> Normalizes telemetry from T.A.P.S. and other data sources for rapid enrichment and analysis.</li>
                <li><strong>Shared Intelligence:</strong> Threat detections and insights from one defended site immediately strengthen all others, forming a collective defense network.</li>
                <li><strong>Operational Affordability:</strong> Shared licensing and cloud-native infrastructure reduce per-operator cost while expanding analytical reach.</li>
              </ul>
